Our story.

The Founding

2019-09-09 - Starting a company is fun!

Tomás and Bjorn representing the academic side, Jenny and Mikael the engineering side, we four found the CSD parent company, Mother. "To bring cutting edge neuroscience techniques from the lab to the clinic".



Growth and Development

2019-10-31 - Starting a company is fun!

Another neuroscientist added to the team (Ana), we are now five. We join the Karolinska Institutet Innovations START group.

Big data

2020-02-02 - Starting a company is fun!

Mother. AB is founded, and we finish the MVP of our first VR project, depunctualisation, running first test runs and collecting first participant data. Good times.

Corona Strikes

2020-03-04 - Starting a company is fun!

Ana and Tomás return to the lab to run C19 tests at KI (COBAS in Huddinge for Ana and DPCR at SÖS for Tomás). Jenny and Mikey start working on the aftercare iOS app.

It's the money

2020-05-15

We get our first grant (Thanks{" "} SSES!), spend it all on shiny hardware.

A quick pivot

2020-09-25

C19 testing ends, Tomas celebrates the return to work with a journey to demo the latest MVP for Bjorn, who is covid-cocooning deep in the Swedish forest. The meeting inspires the creation of{" "} Hertz. , which goes from concept to functional demo within weeks thanks to Mikael’s hard efforts.{" "}

CSD.

2020-10-20

Cybernetic Systems Development is created as a divison of Mother. to handle the software and hardware side of things.

Do less, more.
